    "87 While proprietary and complexity opacity can be addressed through legal means or expert consultation, 88 the inherent natural opacity of deep learning models presents a more fundamental problem.",
    "It is this fact of natural opacity that gives rise to two fundamental political challenges of black box AI: \"value alignment,\" ensuring system behavior aligns with human values and norms, and \"legitimation,\" justifying the use of opaque, uninterpretable systems in consequential decisionmaking processes that affect individuals and society."
